of even the single bomb
that's hit Sheffield.

1384
01:17:23,264 --> 01:17:25,349
[SOBBING]

1385
01:17:30,938 --> 01:17:32,439
[GIRL] Rosie!

1386
01:17:32,731 --> 01:17:33,731
Rosie!

1387
01:17:34,567 --> 01:17:35,567
Diane!

1388
01:17:36,944 --> 01:17:39,697
[PEOPLE GROANING]

1389
01:17:48,164 --> 01:17:50,332
[COUGHING]

1390
01:17:59,133 --> 01:18:01,385
[SCREAMING]

1391
01:18:08,893 --> 01:18:10,227
[MAN] Listen...

1392
01:18:10,519 --> 01:18:13,647
[SHOUTING AND GROANING]

1393
01:18:45,721 --> 01:18:48,182
[COUGHING]

1394
01:18:48,474 --> 01:18:52,228
[MAN] By this time, without
drugs, water or bandages,

1395
01:18:52,519 --> 01:18:55,356
without electricity or
medical support facilities,

1396
